/// FailoverQuorum contains the information about the current failover quorum status of a PG cluster. It
/// is updated by the instance manager of the primary node and reset to zero by the operator to trigger
/// an update.
///
/// This module was generated from the CustomResourceDefinition at
/// <https://raw.githubusercontent.com/cloudnative-pg/cloudnative-pg/v1.29.1/config/crd/kustomization.yaml>.
